name: Pineapple + Smoked Jackfruit Pizza
instructions: 1. Cook spaghetti in boiling water until al dente. 2. In a separate pan, fry bacon until crisp. 3. Beat eggs and mix in grated Parmesan cheese. 4. Drain spaghetti and mix with bacon. 5. Pour egg and cheese mixture over spaghetti and toss until coated. 6. Serve immediately with a sprinkle of black pepper.

comments.comment: This recipe is amazing! The combination of flavors is perfect.
I tried this last night and it turned out great. Definitely making it again!

name: Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken with Quinoa Salad
instructions: 1. Marinate chicken with olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, and herbs for 30 minutes. 2. Grill until cooked through. 3. Cook quinoa and mix with cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and spinach. 4. Top with grilled chicken and a drizzle of olive oil.

comments.comment: Refreshing and light! Great for summer nights.
Excellent protein-packed meal after workouts.

name: Beef and Sweet Potato Power Bowl
instructions: 1. Roast sweet potato cubes with olive oil and paprika. 2. Cook ground beef in a skillet with onions and garlic. 3. Combine beef, sweet potatoes, spinach, and avocado in a bowl. 4. Drizzle with lemon-tahini dressing.
